version_description: Here's the tab for Same Girl, an unreleased Taylor Swift song. It's different from the original but still sounds good. This is an easy way to play it. It's my first tab ever so I hope there's not too much mistake in it :).
This one has more chords(em7, bm). With these the version gets a more interesting melody.
I believe that my chords for this song are better than the ones that have been submitted and more correct
Play the Bsus4 chord by playing a Bm chord but leaving the B and high E string open (i.e. remove your index finger off the bottom of the barre and take your middle finger off the B string).
I've changed the chords in the verses and a little in the chorus, also corrected lyrics :).
This song is in the key of E.
